---
import { siteData } from '../data/site';
---

<footer id="lokasi" class="bg-brand-text text-brand-bg pt-16 pb-8 border-t border-brand-secondary/25">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
      
      <!-- Contact and Brand Info Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-6">
        <!-- Logo (White / Light Version) -->
        <a href="/" class="inline-block group focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-primary rounded-lg" aria-label="Beranda Gubuk Kuliner">
          <!-- Filtered logo to look lighter/white for contrast on dark background -->
          <img 
            src="/assets/img/logo.svg" 
            alt="Logo Gubuk Kuliner" 
            width="180" 
            height="72" 
            class="h-14 w-auto brightness-200 contrast-125 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105" 
          />
        </a>

        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-brand-bg/85 leading-relaxed">
          Gubuk Kuliner menyajikan menu rumahan lezat, halal, dan higienis khas cita rasa nusantara. Siap menemani makan siang, sore, hingga malam Anda di Kelurahan Madurejo.
        </p>

        <!-- Details Grid -->
        <div class="space-y-4 pt-2">
          
          <!-- Location Details -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand-primary/15 text-brand-primary border border-brand-primary/20 flex-shrink-0">
              📍
            </span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-extrabold text-brand-primary text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Lokasi Kami</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-bg/90 leading-snug">{siteData.address}</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Contact Details -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand-primary/15 text-brand-primary border border-brand-primary/20 flex-shrink-0">
              📞
            </span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-extrabold text-brand-primary text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Menerima Pesanan</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-bg/90 leading-snug">
                <a href={siteData.waLink} class="hover:text-brand-primary hover:underline transition-all">+{siteData.whatsapp}</a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Operational Time -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand-primary/15 text-brand-primary border border-brand-primary/20 flex-shrink-0">
              ⏰
            </span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-extrabold text-brand-primary text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Jam Operasional</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-bg/90 leading-snug">Buka Setiap Hari s/d Pukul {siteData.openUntil} WIB</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Maps Link Button -->
        <div class="pt-2">
          <a 
            href={siteData.mapsUrl}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-2xl font-bold text-sm bg-brand-primary text-brand-text hover:bg-brand-bg hover:text-brand-text active:scale-95 shadow-md transition-all"
            aria-label="Buka peta lokasi di Google Maps"
          >
            🗺️ Buka Google Maps
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Map Embed Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-primary font-display">Peta Interaktif</h3>
        
        <!-- Google Map Embed Wrapper -->
        <div class="relative w-full overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border-2 border-brand-secondary/30 shadow-lg" style="aspect-ratio: 16/10;">
          <iframe
            src={siteData.mapsEmbedUrl}
            class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full border-0"
            allowfullscreen=""
            loading="lazy"
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
            title="Lokasi Warung Gubuk Kuliner"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-xs text-brand-bg/70 leading-relaxed italic text-right">
          *Untuk kenyamanan drive-thru atau makan di tempat, Anda bisa melakukan pemesanan via WA + DP terlebih dahulu.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Copyright Divider -->
    <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-brand-bg/10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-xs sm:text-sm text-brand-bg/60">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-2 text-center">
        <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Gubuk Kuliner. Hak Cipta Dilindungi.</p>
        <p>
          Kolaborasi CSR <a href="https://ahliweb.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-primary hover:underline transition-colors">ahliweb.com</a>
          <span class="mx-1">•</span>
          <a href="/license" class="hover:text-brand-primary hover:underline transition-colors">Lisensi</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <a href="#menu" class="hover:text-brand-primary hover:underline transition-colors">Menu</a>
        <span>•</span>
        <a href="#faq" class="hover:text-brand-primary hover:underline transition-colors">FAQ</a>
        <span>•</span>
        <a href={siteData.waLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-brand-primary hover:underline transition-colors">Kontak WA</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</footer>
